race.comment: MEAN APPROACH (4) resumes here but has yet to miss a drum in three fresh attempts and has revved up for this with a recent Gatton trial victory. Handles all going and looks a strong chance to kick off the campaign on the right note. The well-named SPEEDY ONE (8) saves his best form for this sprint journey with three wins and a second from six attempts. Will be rock-hard fit for this and should prove very hard to toss. BONDED AFFAIR (1) goes well for hoop Thompson who has three wins and three placings from just six steers. Include in calculations. VEGAS RAIDER (9) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and may make his presence felt. XPRESSO (5) next in line from the astute Vandyke barn.
